  "title": "A star-like UFO was spotted moving vertically in Ceilândia-DF [1995]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/30/a-star-like-ufo-was-spotted-moving-vertically-in-ceilandia-df-1995/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1jp",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MAY 16th, 1995</strong>. Time: 20h05. Duration: not determined. In Ceilandia, Distrito Federal, several people spotted an unidentified flying object with a round shape, red in color and appeared to be &#8220;the size of the Morning Star&#8221; when seen in the sky. According to witnesses, the UFO was moving vertically, descending slowly from a high altitude. The sighting was carried out with binoculars in a clear sky.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.396. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador no Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>MAY 16th, 1995. Time: 20h05. Duration: not determined. In Ceilandia, Distrito Federal, several people spotted an unidentified flying object with a round shape, red in color and appeared to be &#8220;the size of the Morning Star&#8221; when seen in the sky. According to witnesses, the UFO was moving vertically, descending slowly from a high altitude. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
